// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0564 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 5cd88777-4094-5d5a-9613-86e51a970dfc

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
